Since he heard Kitkat was awake by now, Blackfang whispered something
in Cam's audio receptor.

Blackfang: Why don't you open the door and ask her if she wants to stay?

--- In nbwrpg@yahoogroups.com, "raccoon7679" <logomorph@h...> wrote:
> KitKat::
> 
> She was in the Cr chamber, reliving her old memories.  She was 
> trapped under the rubble from the maximal base. She couldn't move and 
> her air for her systems was getting thin. She started pounding on 
> parts of the collapsed ceiling, She yelled and screamed. Then she 
> heard a voice on her commlink. It was megatron. "You served me well 
> KitKat, but you will be remembered as dying well in battle. Farwell 
> KitKat."  and the link went dead.  She screamed and pounded on the 
> ceiling. "YOU SLAGGING PIECES OF RUSTED SCRAP METAL, HOW DARE YOU 
> LEAVE ME TO DIE DOWN HERE, I'LL COME BACK AND KILL YOU SO HELP ME I 
> WILL!"
> 
> Her words could be heard outside the chamber as she kicked and 
> screamed. 
> 
> She pounded her fist againt the wall of the chamber, when the ringing 
> of the metal being pounded woke her up. She looked around to see 
> herself in a cr chamber. She relaxed and wondered how she ended up 
> here.  She gently knocked from the inside of the chamber. "Hello? 
> anyone out there? Can I get out now?"
